narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Laura Cabadas is a Social Worker provider based in Elmhurst, IL. From 2018-01 through 2019-08, this provider received $207K in Medicaid payments across 3K claims serving 1K beneficiaries, billing 2 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: Bills 2.0× the national median for 97530 (97530), at $66 per claim vs. the median of $33, placing them above the 75th percentile.
87% of billing is concentrated in 97530 (97530), indicating significant specialization in this service.
Billing stopped in 2019-08, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.
